{"tid":197723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國首艘自製航母傳23日下水 網友票選命名「台灣號」","createTime":"2017-04-12T05:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T06:07:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1622ecd3a10af416ed9cf819b16e48601c9a84ae","tid":197723,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:11:57.000Z","msg":"陸首艘自製航母傳23日下水 網友票選命名「台灣號」 <br />\n<br />\nSETN／綜合報導 <br />\n<br />\n中國大陸自製的航空母艦，傳將在23日下水服役，但名稱遲遲未定。陸媒《鳳凰網》就航 母名稱進行網路票選，沒想到第一名竟然是「台灣號」。 ▲<br />\n<br />\n大陸首艘自製航母，傳23日將下水服役。（圖／翻攝自大陸新浪網） 外傳中國大陸選在23日海軍節，讓引以為傲的首艘自製「001A型」航母下水，它在執行任 務時最多可搭載36架殲-15艦載機，是遼寧艦的1.5倍。 不過，最讓大家好奇的就是航空母艦的名稱，鳳凰網特別舉辦票選，得票最高的竟是「台 灣號」，得票率逼近4成為38%，其次為「北京號」的21%與「廣東號」的14％。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1cj3z1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1cj3z1&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e10339c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1cj3z1</a>"},{"pid":"f15556de5daa134ae43fda8dc96b16f514b9f45f","tid":197723,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"咁無志氣<br />\n緊係叫美國號啦"},{"pid":"23cdf7f3f9f033e17b428bdf4e2ab9ffa36f2d6b","tid":197723,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"好易令人誤會係屬於台灣<br />\n等睇大陸班智障改加上中國兩字<br />\n&quot;中國台灣號&quot;"},{"pid":"641733904155c0bbc70a394c789c7542e4786b5c","tid":197723,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"「台灣好」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c240b3f5f2090e908ddda14d0892758517d92222","tid":197723,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁無志氣<br />\n緊係叫美國號啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國省號"},{"pid":"e8248592dcf950ef2c631d46339928be728aa83c","tid":197723,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"台灣藍波萬"},{"pid":"04a7716da